article_titles_hint: Ne èle nyatiwo hem va le woƒe tanyawo nu la, kpɔe nyuie be tanyaa de pɛpɛpɛ eye nèŋlɔ ɖeka ɖe fli ɖeka dzi.

footer: lɔlɔ̃nu faa dɔwɔlawoe wɔ %s, enɔ %s dzi eye woɖe egɔme le %s.

import_articles_prompt: Taflatsɛ ŋlɔ Wikipedia {em_start}ƒe nyati ƒe tanyawo{em_end} ne nahe wo va, fli ɖeka ɖeka le afi si dze le ete:
import_petscan_category_tip: Mɔfiame: Nyati siwo le hatsotso {category} la me koe le {tooltitle} eme. Ne èdi be nudidia nade to wu la, àte ŋu azã PetSkan atsɔ adi nyati siwo le hatsotso ma ko me.
import_petscan_intro: {em_start}PetSkan{em_end} nye dɔwɔnu si wotsɔ dia nu le Wikipedia hetsɔ tia nyati siwo adze. PetSkan naa dzeside nudidi ɖe sia ɖe ale be woate ŋu afɔ ŋuɖoɖoawo ayi dɔwɔnu buubuwo dzi.
import_petscan_prompt: Taflatsɛ {link_start}wɔ wò nudidia le PetSkan{link_end} me eye nàda eƒe dzeside ɖe ete afi sia:
instructions_details: Zi %s dzi wòayi Wikipedia ne nàtrɔ asi le mɔfiaɖoɖoa ŋu alo zi %s dzi ne nàkpɔ bubu. Kpɔ %s ne nyabiasewo le asiwò. Eme nenyo na wò!
instructions_goal: Wikipedia mɔfiaɖoɖo si le ete la {link_start} mekpɔ nyatakatsoƒe si ŋu kakaɖedzi le o{link_end}. Àte ŋu adi ɖea?
custom_end_copy_link: Àte ŋu akɔpi kadodo si le etame ahamae na amewo woazã, alo {link_start}ne nàʋui fifia{link_end}!
custom_failed: Taflatsɛ, mete ŋu wɔ wò {tooltitle} la o alo mekpɔ naneke o!
custom_import_prompt: Afi kae nàdi be yeafɔ nyatiwo tsoe?
custom_intro: Àte ŋu atrɔ asi le {tooltitle} ŋu ne èfɔ nyatiwo va eme. Esia awɔe be nàma wo kple amewo ale be woate ŋu aʋu nyati siwo le {tooltitle} la ko.
custom_notice: Èʋu {tooltitle} si nyati aɖewo ko le. {link_start}Zi afi sia{link_end} ne nàyi afi si nyatiwo sɔ gbɔ le {tooltitle}.
custom_please_wait: Taflatsɛ ele dɔ wɔm le wò {tooltitle} ŋu. Axɔ miniti ʋɛ aɖewo…
introduction: Kpe ɖe mía ŋu míakpɔ tsoƒe na Wikipedia nyatiwo!
js-custom-numbers: Mɔfiameɖoɖo si tso {{PLURAL:$1|nyati|nyati}} $1 me la le eme eye anɔ anyi {{PLURAL:$2|ŋkeke|ŋkeke}} $2:
js-leaving-custom: Ètrɔ yina {tooltitle} si nyatiwo sɔ gbɔ le. Èdii nenema?
lead_section_hint: Nuŋɔŋlɔ sia nye nyatia ƒe akpa vevitɔ ƒe akpa aɖe, eya ta ne èlɔ̃e nànɔ ŋkɔe. Taflatsɛ kpɔ %s hena nyatakaka bubuwo.
leaderboard_description: Ezalã siwo ɖɔ mɔfiaɖoɖowo ɖo to {tooltitle} dzi le {ŋkeke} ŋkeke siwo va yi me la woe nye esi. Akpe kakaka!
page_not_found_text: Axa si dim nèle la megali o — ɖewohĩ eke ɖe nuyɔyɔ sia ŋu xoxo? Trɔ yi %s hena nu bubuwo!
petscan_hint: Ne èzã PetSkan le nu dim la, ƒo asa na nu siwo didi axɔ ɣeyiɣi didi hafi PetSkan la ate ŋu ake ɖe wo ŋu eye kpɔ egbɔ be yeŋlɔ URL alo PSID wòde pɛpɛpɛ.
